dc_title_s: PSAP Service Area Boundaries Manitowoc County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: [The public-safety answering point (PSAP) boundary for Manitowoc County. It includes the portion of the City of Kiel in Calumet County.] This data layer represents 911 Public Safety Answering Point (PSAP) service area boundaries in Manitowoc county, Wisconsin in 2020. According to the National Emergency Number Association (NENA), a Public Safety Answering Point (PSAP) is a facility equipped and staffed to receive 9-1-1 calls. The service area is the geographic area within which a 911 call placed using a landline is answered at the associated PSAP.
uw_supplemental_s: Augment original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
